finikMapProductDescription: Finik is a terminal map. Discover, add terminals and earn points

mailForPasswordReset: Enter mail to receive a code to reset your password
OTPExplanation: Enter the received one-time password to verify your phone number
passwordNoUppercase: Password should have an uppercase letter
passwordNoLowercaseChars: Password should have a lowercase letter
passwordNoSpecialCharacters: Password should have a special character
passwordTooShort: Password should have at least 8 character
